Dialogue: 2,0:00:02.79,0:00:07.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.03,0:00:10.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let’s get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 2,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kazutoyo Koyabu
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.13,0:00:21.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's Koyabu  \N-Thank you very much
Dialogue: 2,0:00:22.26,0:00:23.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So let's get right to the point
Dialogue: 2,0:00:23.59,0:00:27.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have any of you here ever had to fake something for a show since you entered the industry?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.73,0:00:31.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, faked a lot
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The best time was with a psychic medium
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.65,0:00:37.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doing a show in a place where there are rumors of ghosts
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.01,0:00:40.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was said that there was a ghost in a phone booth there
Dialogue: 2,0:00:40.88,0:00:43.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we went to the phone booth
Dialogue: 2,0:00:43.91,0:00:45.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then came a sound of jingling bells
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.99,0:00:48.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They said it was the spirit's voice
Dialogue: 2,0:00:48.56,0:00:52.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I realized it was the psychic hitting the side of the phone booth with small stones
Dialogue: 2,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've learned since then
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.93,0:00:58.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Psychic programs are just lies
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.85,0:01:00.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what they do
Dialogue: 2,0:01:00.37,0:01:04.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently, regulations in the TV industry have become more and more strict
Dialogue: 2,0:01:04.80,0:01:10.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fake information in a literal sense has all but disappeared
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.00,0:01:14.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, today I bring this hypothesis about such fraud
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.90,0:01:22.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Artists who are required to participate in misleading TV shows can't help helping the program
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has this been done before?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, a similar theory was done two years ago
Dialogue: 2,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time it is a comprehensive upgrade, single-cut verification
Dialogue: 2,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will the performers risk their lives for the sake of the show and blatantly mislead
Dialogue: 2,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In this era of various rules and regulations
Dialogue: 2,0:01:36.66,0:01:39.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do they dare to cross the red line of moral degradation?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Emotions are strangely high.  \N-Does it still exist?
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, I want to reveal the truth in broad daylight
Dialogue: 2,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why are you so angry all of a sudden?\N  -Yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:01:48.53,0:01:52.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To sum up, next we will verify the taboo of fraud
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.86,0:01:58.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also, for businesses that borrow performers' names
Dialogue: 2,0:01:58.20,0:02:02.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No matter how unpleasant the content, will they accept if the pay is high enough?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:18.02,0:02:29.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Artists who are required to participate in misleading TV shows can't help helping the program
Dialogue: 2,0:02:30.44,0:02:34.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, the first difficulty level 1 target is
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.73,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The embodiment of tenderness
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.73,0:02:38.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ganbare Luya's Yoshiko
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The stage for this validation is
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.44,0:02:46.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko and Shouinji introduce the stores they frequent
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fradulent program is set up in such a way
Dialogue: 2,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to hear about the stores frequented by these two people?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:50.54,0:02:55.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we took a look at the stores Yoshiko frequented beforehand, but
Dialogue: 2,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The trip was accidentally double booked
Dialogue: 2,0:03:00.26,0:03:03.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, she's informed that one of the stores is reserved for Shouinji
Dialogue: 2,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And is unable to participate in the location recording
Dialogue: 2,0:03:06.96,0:03:10.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we want to talk a little bit about it. \N -OK
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stores frequented by Shouinji
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.89,0:03:19.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Originally, there was one that wasn't possible, but we repeatedly negotiated
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.37,0:03:21.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It took a lot of effort to get permission
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.25,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A tough situation to say no to
Dialogue: 2,0:03:22.58,0:03:27.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's told that one of Shouinji's choices was difficult
Dialogue: 2,0:03:29.00,0:03:34.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The suggestion is to present it as a shop that Yoshiko often goes to
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Making for an embarrassing request
Dialogue: 2,0:03:38.32,0:03:42.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The shop that Shouinji often goes to
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.26,0:03:47.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would it be okay to present it as one of the places you regularly frequent?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, I see, I see
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although a little surprised
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The offer is accepted smoothly
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.65,0:03:56.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd turn out like this
Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.81,0:04:03.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This place's speciality is tomato noodles
Dialogue: 2,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Understood
Dialogue: 2,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Have you ever eaten tomato noodles?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.32,0:04:12.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Never, I have never eaten tomato noodles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To sum up, Yoshiko knows nothing
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.57,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.28,0:04:20.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And she's told this is a confidential matter known only to the producer
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.48,0:04:22.21,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It happens
Dialogue: 2,0:04:21.77,0:04:23.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shouinji doesn't know either? \N-No
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.01,0:04:27.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With none of the staff supposedly informed
