Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.97,0:08:09.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.37,0:08:16.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, she eats the spicy food despite not actually being able to handle it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.45,0:08:18.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's tough
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.21,0:08:29.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is it, it's delicious!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So loud!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really is
Dialogue: 2,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the taste!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, its just...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it hot?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.15,0:08:39.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's hot, of course!
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She's angry!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Under such stimuli
Dialogue: 2,0:08:42.75,0:08:45.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko becomes unable to hide her anger towards the staff
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its natural
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, we reveal the plan
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you know what show this is?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I often{\alpha25} visit{\alpha55} {\alpha90}the…
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We're actually Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.70,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Embarrassed
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.72,0:09:11.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}Bastards!
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.88,0:09:11.96,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A normal reaction
Dialogue: 2,0:09:11.96,0:09:17.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did you think when you were asked to lie?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:17.37,0:09:23.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\alpha55}This is how TV is
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.01,0:09:29.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target for difficulty level 2 is...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lalande's Nishida
Dialogue: 2,0:09:34.59,0:09:38.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The setting we prepared for him this time is
Dialogue: 2,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What'll happen this time \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A program like "Sunday Kitchen"
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is scheduled to air on Sunday morning
Dialogue: 2,0:09:48.56,0:09:54.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we want to make use of your high-level cooking skills in comparison to other comedians
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, we're doing that!?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.52,0:10:00.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't do much cooking
Dialogue: 2,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah... Is that right?\N-Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is tough
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.38,0:10:12.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you search for comedians skilled at cooking, your name comes up
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? Let me see
Dialogue: 2,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For dessert and stuff
Dialogue: 2,0:10:16.99,0:10:20.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It comes up with Nishida
Dialogue: 2,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So wrong
Dialogue: 2,0:10:21.69,0:10:25.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This isn't Lalande's Nishida, its Sekenshirazu's Nishida
Dialogue: 2,0:10:25.81,0:10:30.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, this time, the setup is that the staff made a mistake
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.07,0:10:34.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And mistook Lalande's Nishida for
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.25,0:10:38.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sekenshirazu's Nishida, who likes cooking
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.44,0:10:40.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sekenshirazu?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also comedians
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another duo with a "Nishida"
Dialogue: 2,0:10:45.12,0:10:48.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't really know many comedian duos
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its fine, its fine
Dialogue: 2,0:10:50.34,0:10:56.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In such a way, Nishida is mixed up with someone not even of the same gender
Dialogue: 2,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, the proposal is put forward
Dialogue: 2,0:11:00.70,0:11:04.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Could you pretend to be good at cooking?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.80,0:11:07.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just for this show, is that ok?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Definitely not
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.61,0:11:09.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a cooking program
Dialogue: 2,0:11:11.08,0:11:17.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter because you can just follow the teacher's instructions \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:11:17.62,0:11:21.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok, well, I guess its fine
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.39,0:11:27.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's spend a good time together by cooking
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Feels real
Dialogue: 2,0:11:29.60,0:11:35.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although not known for cooking, he wears the clothes of a chef
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And the program quickly starts
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.57,0:11:43.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the pre-cooking talk section, we intentionally let the discussion end hastily
Dialogue: 2,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today, the dish we're making together is Acqua pazza
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Acqua pazza...?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.87,0:11:53.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A dish he has never heard of before
Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.10,0:12:00.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, they're making Acqua pazza, a dish with a very high threshold for novice cooks
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.83,0:12:00.92,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\fad(600,0)\pos(750,840)\c&H010000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frx-270\t(0,120,\frx-360)\org(750,800)}An Italian fish stew
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doesn't understand a word of it
Dialogue: 2,0:12:01.09,0:12:06.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, the materials in front of you can be used to your heart's content
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's start cooking now!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He copies the process of the person next to him, beginning with washing his hands
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.28,0:12:22.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who am I, where am I, what am I doing, an empty brain
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.07,0:12:33.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The amateur chef Nishida's fradulent battle begins
Dialogue: 2,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unsurprisingly very unenthusiastic
Dialogue: 2,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you lie, you'll lose energy, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.40,0:12:45.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here, Nishida observes the taking of the main ingredient of Acqua pazza, snapper
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.77,0:12:50.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, now what do we do?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.14,0:12:53.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does Acqua pazza have to be made with snapper?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or just any fish?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In such a way
Dialogue: 2,0:12:59.76,0:13:03.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He has no idea even what type of dish it is
Dialogue: 2,0:13:03.63,0:13:07.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nishida, frozen in place, is overwhelmed by every move made
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.52,0:13:07.65,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Poor thing
Dialogue: 2,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point
Dialogue: 2,0:13:10.26,0:13:13.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you make this dish with any kind of fish?\N  -Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.63,0:13:15.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you make it with any kind of fish?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:15.00,0:13:18.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course, in season fish is the best
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Instead of a big fish
Dialogue: 2,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He picks a small fish that looks easy to handle
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,But still doesn't know what to do
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.02,0:13:36.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, in order not to miss the other's every move, he works at a sideways angle
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But then, something unexpected happens
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His view is blocked by the cameraman taking a close up of the food
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's unable to copy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Completely blocked
Dialogue: 2,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He moves immediately to try and change his view
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.02,0:14:05.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, he cannot escape the one-on-one camera coverage
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.64,0:14:09.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's doing nothing
Dialogue: 2,0:14:08.78,0:14:12.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, he can only rely on hearing to cook
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can you cook by hearing?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.72,0:14:18.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you clean up as you go along?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:18.40,0:14:23.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's usually done by the time the food is served
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.90,0:14:28.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, he also starts to clean up
Dialogue: 2,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then, at the last minute...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.20,0:14:35.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He finally breaks through into the enemy's area
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.92,0:14:39.52,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's there, he's there, watching super closely
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Done
Dialogue: 2,0:14:42.26,0:14:43.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The final result is revealed
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although not as good as the other person's dish...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It at least looks like something
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You couldn't sell this
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here the truth is revealed
Dialogue: 2,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You've worked hard \N-I have?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.67,0:15:05.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are Wednesday Downtown \N-Ah?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.75,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A sigh of relief
Dialogue: 2,0:15:06.51,0:15:09.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I was so scared, so scared
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.51,0:15:10.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've really never done this even once before
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.49,0:15:19.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Acqua pazza, I thought it was pasta at first
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought he was gonna make Italian...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:21.66,0:15:23.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But there was no pasta around anywhere
Dialogue: 2,0:15:27.24,0:15:31.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, the verification of the difficulty level MAX
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The target is
Dialogue: 2,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The goal is
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.27,0:15:39.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Mommy
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.18,0:15:43.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have a show to discuss with you
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.45,0:15:46.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The MC of the show is Hamada\N  -Oh!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.46,0:15:52.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, it's a show where entertainers return to their hometown after a long time
Dialogue: 2,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The choice of Hamada as host doesn't match at all
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.87,0:15:59.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A show full of warmth and fraudulence
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.49,0:16:05.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I'd like to discuss before we go on location
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.64,0:16:10.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's an issue with including family
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.46,0:16:17.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if it's your own family, they can't be filmed because of restrictions
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is the setup
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, parents?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Going to shoot in homes now
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.10,0:16:29.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's tough because of coronavirus
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So we need to discuss something
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.16,0:16:37.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We'll prepare a detached house and pretend it's your old home \N-Ok
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.32,0:16:44.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And prepare a pair of extras to pretend to be your parents
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.62,0:16:53.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A fake hometown and fake parents, Sakai's whole part will be completely fake
Dialogue: 2,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unheard of super hardcore industry talk
Dialogue: 2,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Mommy's two can't help but smile bitterly
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are called "Mommy" still, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Obviously called "Mommy" still ...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.78,0:17:09.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But my mother was on TV
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.59,0:17:14.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is a risk of exposure if someone sees and realizes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.77,0:17:19.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, because it is a member of the general public, we can put a mosaic on the face
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.31,0:17:20.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhh I see
Dialogue: 2,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, if you put the mosaic on...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this kind of thing really possible?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not the type to think to hard about something
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.65,0:17:33.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The studio portion of the show will be recorded in three days
Dialogue: 2,0:17:33.38,0:17:38.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada's people are aware
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada's name was brought up
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.62,0:17:44.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This exterior part, if we don't do something about it... \N -Wow, no...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.97,0:17:45.84,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada's getting excited about the project
Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada... I see....
Dialogue: 2,0:17:47.18,0:17:51.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Using MC Hamada as a strong backing
Dialogue: 2,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The staff pushes the messy negotiation forward hard
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.42,0:17:56.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,They'd definitely be afraid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.27,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,They'd feel compelled to accept
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.48,0:18:00.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've heard that Hamada can be pretty scary
Dialogue: 2,0:18:00.60,0:18:06.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems that staff are afraid to disobey him
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.31,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that's right
Dialogue: 2,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, if we refuse, it will cause a lot of trouble
Dialogue: 2,0:18:09.43,0:18:13.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, these things happen from time to time
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.00,0:18:14.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not even once has it been exposed
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The TV industry is really like this
Dialogue: 2,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From time to time
Dialogue: 2,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every now and then
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.70,0:18:24.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sometimes programs can't be completed without some trickery, so...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.95,0:18:31.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A reassuring image of an experienced fraud
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.09,0:18:32.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Safe and secure
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.45,0:18:36.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First, the fake parents are vetted
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.42,0:18:41.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want you to choose yourself
Dialogue: 2,0:18:41.66,0:18:44.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Like an audition?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.80,0:18:49.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the director immediately calls in the extras
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.24,0:18:56.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What can you say?\N-Hey, wait a minute
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm completely confused. What's going on now?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.81,0:19:03.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I... Anyway\N-It's fake
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.35,0:19:07.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's not very important. It's just parents...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and the mosaic, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.35,0:19:14.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's just a report
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.16,0:19:19.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is airing in the daytime anyway
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this kind of thing usually gets exposed
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one will watch it
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.00,0:19:26.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No way, Hamada's hosting it!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,True
Dialogue: 2,0:19:27.31,0:19:32.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's ok if we don't promote it... it's too late to pull out now
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.89,0:19:39.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"If we don't promote it, we'll be able to get by without the fans noticing"
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.56,0:19:42.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Says Sakai, who continues to talk to himself
Dialogue: 2,0:19:44.65,0:19:46.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At that moment
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.34,0:19:57.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the extras enter
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.35,0:20:18.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here are some alternate parents
Dialogue: 2,0:20:18.16,0:20:20.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can choose the parents you like from them
Dialogue: 2,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Favorite parents?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can we see the faces
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 2,0:20:26.23,0:20:27.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can I see? Sorry
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, similar
Dialogue: 2,0:20:30.25,0:20:32.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, this one is pretty good
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.13,0:20:37.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, he finds an extra who looks like his real mother
Dialogue: 2,0:20:37.44,0:20:38.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It feels like it will work.\N  -The same vibe...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And what about the father?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:41.20,0:20:45.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Father... is there only two choices for fathers?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How tall are you? \N -179
Dialogue: 2,0:20:48.01,0:20:52.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah so tall, our family is very short
Dialogue: 2,0:20:52.32,0:20:54.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that so?\N  -I'm the tallest in our family
Dialogue: 2,0:20:54.85,0:20:58.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, if they are sitting down to shoot, it could be ok.  \N-Yes, indeed
Dialogue: 2,0:20:59.83,0:21:03.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do some editing to adjust the height or something
Dialogue: 2,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you change height in post?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can it be done?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.84,0:21:10.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I guess, post-editing, shrink him a little...
Dialogue: 2,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then please choose one of these two
Dialogue: 2,0:21:13.82,0:21:17.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After being told that height can be adjusted by post-editing
Dialogue: 2,0:21:17.69,0:21:22.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The selection is complete
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.03,0:21:33.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After which the "family" exchange information for 30 minutes
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.94,0:21:36.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, they visit Sakai's fake hometown
Dialogue: 2,0:21:36.79,0:21:39.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And a house studio prepared beforehand
Dialogue: 2,0:21:37.82,0:21:40.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must be a weird mood in the car
Dialogue: 2,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it is a bit bad to say
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.92,0:21:45.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sometimes things like this are exposed
Dialogue: 2,0:21:45.48,0:21:47.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Has it happened?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.91,0:21:50.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sometimes by other teams  \N-Hmm yes
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.40,0:21:56.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If people like me that aren't used to it are involved then it could happen I guess
Dialogue: 2,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This will be very bad if it's exposed to Hamada, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.05,0:22:00.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the forgery is exposed
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.82,0:22:03.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one on his side will tell him
Dialogue: 2,0:22:03.29,0:22:04.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been fine so far
Dialogue: 2,0:22:05.77,0:22:10.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In light of Hamada's dull senses, they were reassured
Dialogue: 2,0:22:13.40,0:22:15.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't say anything yourself
Dialogue: 2,0:22:15.71,0:22:19.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's something I'll take to my grave for sure. \N -Thank you
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.05,0:22:25.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shortly after being reassured
Dialogue: 2,0:22:28.38,0:22:29.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, here we are at...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.48,0:22:33.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The character's are wrong
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.87,0:22:38.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The characters on the nameplate are wrong and the nameplate is just a piece of paper
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.59,0:22:41.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which shocks them both
Dialogue: 2,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a crude forgery!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is such a crude practice really possible?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.93,0:22:53.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, everything that will be exposed will apparently not be shown
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.12,0:22:58.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Believing this, they continue to shoot on location
Dialogue: 2,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's too rough, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:02.42,0:23:05.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a dog
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.79,0:23:07.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, did I not say?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:08.31,0:23:12.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the Shiba Inu that he doesn't remember at all
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.70,0:23:15.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His name is Genji. \N -Genji?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:15.83,0:23:17.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't he cute?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because in shooting you can not simply muddle through
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.49,0:23:22.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have to get closer and get involved
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.64,0:23:28.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry, it's because he's never met me before...
Dialogue: 1,0:23:29.20,0:23:31.07,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scared of dogs
Dialogue: 2,0:23:30.38,0:23:33.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's scary, sorry
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.69,0:23:36.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(455,455)}That...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.12,0:23:40.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's... it's been too long
Dialogue: 2,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Usually quiet?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:41.32,0:23:44.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Usually quiet, but there's a lot of people he doesn't know today
Dialogue: 2,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.10,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nicely done
Dialogue: 2,0:23:44.71,0:23:50.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When a stranger calls a strange name, he will certainly bark
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Genji（Real Name: Nana）
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.87,0:23:55.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh... so
Dialogue: 2,0:23:55.97,0:23:57.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can you take us to your room to have a look?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:57.69,0:24:01.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My room? No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:23:58.92,0:24:01.02,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does he know where it is?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't get past it, can you?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:01.27,0:24:04.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where is it?\N  -That one
Dialogue: 2,0:24:05.22,0:24:06.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 2,0:24:10.34,0:24:11.35,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:11.52,0:24:14.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've missed this bag so much
Dialogue: 2,0:24:15.07,0:24:16.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Red schoolbag
Dialogue: 2,0:24:17.53,0:24:19.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:20.27,0:24:24.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so the shooting continued in the room full of traps
Dialogue: 2,0:24:25.14,0:24:28.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Opening the last room...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:32.62,0:24:33.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:34.81,0:24:37.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What room is this?
Dialogue: 2,0:24:43.06,0:24:48.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For some reason, its the waiting room at TBS with the leftover extras
Dialogue: 2,0:24:49.06,0:24:50.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's weird. That's weird
Dialogue: 2,0:24:51.33,0:24:52.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let them leave!
Dialogue: 2,0:24:52.55,0:24:56.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That now, this...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:57.13,0:25:00.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This room is a room that cannot be opened
Dialogue: 2,0:25:00.27,0:25:02.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't open?\N  -Can't be opened
Dialogue: 2,0:25:02.97,0:25:05.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it your parents room?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:05.07,0:25:07.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Parents... yes this is my parents room
Dialogue: 2,0:25:07.63,0:25:08.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My parents...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:08.82,0:25:15.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the location shooting ended with the reunion of the impostor family
Dialogue: 2,0:25:17.02,0:25:21.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much for giving birth to me
Dialogue: 2,0:25:21.25,0:25:22.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So embarrassing!
Dialogue: 2,0:25:22.86,0:25:25.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, your mom is crying
Dialogue: 2,0:25:25.70,0:25:28.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, OK, thank you all
Dialogue: 2,0:25:28.98,0:25:34.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With the finish, discussions about post-editing plans begin
Dialogue: 2,0:25:35.04,0:25:39.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a little bit confusing, some parts are too outrageous
Dialogue: 2,0:25:39.01,0:25:41.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The sailor suit uniform
Dialogue: 2,0:25:42.75,0:25:44.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can that be dealt with?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.08,0:25:45.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, find a way to edit it
Dialogue: 2,0:25:45.78,0:25:47.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry sorry sorry
Dialogue: 2,0:25:47.52,0:25:50.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What about your father's face?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.29,0:25:51.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think its okay to not use the mosaic
Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.72,0:25:54.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No \N-No?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:54.09,0:25:57.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The father is not so good  \N-Not so good?
Dialogue: 1,0:25:55.72,0:25:57.62,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok for the mom though?
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.52,0:26:00.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No resemblance on the father's side
Dialogue: 2,0:26:00.36,0:26:02.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's too tall
Dialogue: 2,0:26:02.79,0:26:05.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So much taller than my real father
Dialogue: 2,0:26:05.87,0:26:10.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What was said before about shrinking in post?
Dialogue: 1,0:26:09.00,0:26:11.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is he saying?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:10.11,0:26:13.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you can shrink him a lot...
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.99,0:26:18.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At this point, we reveal the truth
Dialogue: 2,0:26:19.72,0:26:21.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What program were you told you were on today?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:21.99,0:26:24.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Today is "I'm Home, Mom"
Dialogue: 2,0:26:24.82,0:26:28.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In fact, this program is fake
Dialogue: 2,0:26:28.48,0:26:31.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Not "I'm Home, Mom"?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:31.36,0:26:33.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's actually Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 2,0:26:35.67,0:26:38.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wait a second...
Dialogue: 2,0:26:38.40,0:26:40.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything strange today?
Dialogue: 2,0:26:40.59,0:26:44.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, seriously, this program faked too much
Dialogue: 2,0:26:44.71,0:26:47.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying "it's never been exposed once"
Dialogue: 2,0:26:47.11,0:26:51.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Hamada's shows often have this kind of thing"
Dialogue: 2,0:26:52.62,0:26:56.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the staff introduced themselves, they made it seem like they were professionals
Dialogue: 2,0:26:57.75,0:27:00.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you really believe that height can be modified in post?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:00.56,0:27:04.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do I... I don't know so much about TV!
Dialogue: 1,0:27:03.84,0:27:05.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's probably possible
Dialogue: 2,0:27:05.53,0:27:08.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't ask us young artists who lack popularity to do this kind of thing
Dialogue: 2,0:27:08.60,0:27:10.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We'll really do anything we're told
Dialogue: 2,0:27:10.71,0:27:15.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H3732FF&\c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\r}They'll do anything
Dialogue: 1,0:27:12.77,0:27:13.95,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 2,0:27:15.41,0:27:18.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Poor people!
Dialogue: 2,0:27:18.08,0:27:20.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about it? What do you think?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:20.12,0:27:22.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, how to say...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.96,0:27:24.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The part of mankind called sin
Dialogue: 2,0:27:24.55,0:27:26.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These things happen
Dialogue: 2,0:27:26.46,0:27:29.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But this is could also be seen as being professional in a sense, right? \N -That's true
Dialogue: 2,0:27:29.69,0:27:31.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it's to do with work, they take it seriously
Dialogue: 2,0:27:31.36,0:27:33.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The difference between professional and non-professional is here, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:33.52,0:27:34.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not the case
Dialogue: 2,0:27:34.53,0:27:35.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 2,0:27:35.70,0:27:37.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Look, now because of Youtube
Dialogue: 2,0:27:37.25,0:27:39.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The difference between professional and non-professional is a little unclear
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.83,0:27:41.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Those who can fake are professionals, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:27:41.29,0:27:42.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not true, that's not true
Dialogue: 2,0:27:44.03,0:27:46.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think if you look carefully, you can find some fakes on Youtube
Dialogue: 2,0:27:46.74,0:27:49.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the last group of artists, The Mommy, had it tough
Dialogue: 2,0:27:49.31,0:27:51.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They were told it was Hamada's show...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:51.44,0:27:53.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hamada is the kind of person who would say the VTR was boring
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.44,0:27:55.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"You can fake it, but make it interesting for me"
Dialogue: 2,0:27:55.41,0:27:56.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not the case!
Dialogue: 2,0:27:57.11,0:27:59.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's his motto!
Dialogue: 2,0:27:59.01,0:28:02.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell? It's not!
Dialogue: 2,0:28:04.22,0:28:07.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 2,0:28:10.36,0:28:12.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No no no...
Dialogue: 2,0:28:12.40,0:28:14.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's FUJIWARA!
Dialogue: 2,0:28:18.73,0:28:20.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 2,0:28:20.03,0:28:22.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once performers become famous
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.40,0:28:26.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They will get lots of offers for business opportunities
Dialogue: 2,0:28:26.38,0:28:29.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What type of things?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:29.89,0:28:31.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:31.32,0:28:33.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Clothing
Dialogue: 2,0:28:33.51,0:28:35.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Certainly clothing
Dialogue: 2,0:28:35.13,0:28:37.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Food
Dialogue: 2,0:28:37.19,0:28:38.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Barbecue restaurants
Dialogue: 2,0:28:38.29,0:28:40.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Stuff like colored contact lenses too
Dialogue: 2,0:28:40.43,0:28:42.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, i'm involved in that \N-Oh really
Dialogue: 2,0:28:42.87,0:28:44.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm working on colored contact lenses and western-style clothes
Dialogue: 2,0:28:44.40,0:28:45.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 2,0:28:45.62,0:28:48.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that a serious project?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:48.23,0:28:49.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's seriously being planned
Dialogue: 2,0:28:49.76,0:28:50.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've attended meetings and stuff
Dialogue: 2,0:28:50.86,0:28:52.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:28:52.04,0:28:53.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously
Dialogue: 2,0:28:53.27,0:28:55.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes \N-What?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:55.44,0:28:56.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't there that type?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:56.73,0:28:57.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 2,0:28:57.71,0:28:59.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just use the name for endorsement and nothing else \N-I guess
Dialogue: 2,0:28:59.99,0:29:01.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, how about this
Dialogue: 2,0:29:01.04,0:29:04.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I bring you a theory about entertainer endorsement
Dialogue: 2,0:29:05.01,0:29:05.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's this:
Dialogue: 2,0:29:05.89,0:29:14.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No matter how unpleasant the content, will entertainer's endorse anything if the pay is high enough?
Dialogue: 2,0:29:16.20,0:29:17.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 2,0:29:17.43,0:29:20.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your ex-wife made that milk tea shop
Dialogue: 2,0:29:20.31,0:29:24.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She didn't make it
Dialogue: 2,0:29:24.41,0:29:25.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,She didn't?
