Dialogue: 2,0:40:42.45,0:40:44.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super chic  \N-Thank you
Dialogue: 2,0:40:44.55,0:40:47.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Very fashionable \N-Thanks
Dialogue: 2,0:40:47.36,0:40:48.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like it \N-The vibe?
Dialogue: 2,0:40:48.99,0:40:50.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I like it
Dialogue: 2,0:40:50.33,0:40:53.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please turn to the next page
Dialogue: 2,0:40:53.03,0:40:54.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Another option has been prepared
Dialogue: 2,0:40:54.28,0:40:56.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? What is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:40:54.82,0:40:56.50,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is too much, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:40:59.37,0:41:03.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a design that completely highlights Nana Suzuki
Dialogue: 1,0:40:59.50,0:41:02.20,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It fits Teshima Yu's persona at least
Dialogue: 2,0:41:03.84,0:41:05.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm glad, but..
Dialogue: 2,0:41:05.61,0:41:10.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I feel a like it won't do so well
Dialogue: 2,0:41:11.54,0:41:15.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think its a bit unapproachable
Dialogue: 1,0:41:12.72,0:41:14.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,She said it
Dialogue: 1,0:41:14.90,0:41:16.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 2,0:41:16.09,0:41:19.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it will fail
Dialogue: 2,0:41:19.56,0:41:24.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Nana shows clear disapproval of this look
Dialogue: 2,0:41:22.23,0:41:24.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A normal reaction
Dialogue: 2,0:41:24.16,0:41:27.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regarding your fee
Dialogue: 2,0:41:27.27,0:41:29.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If Option A is used
Dialogue: 2,0:41:29.20,0:41:31.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It will use a lot of the budget
Dialogue: 2,0:41:31.01,0:41:33.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand
Dialogue: 2,0:41:33.37,0:41:40.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We can give you about 30,000 yen per month, 30,000 per store
Dialogue: 2,0:41:40.04,0:41:46.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The initial cost of B is not much \N-Ok
Dialogue: 2,0:41:46.81,0:41:50.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you can get 500,000 yen per month for this one
Dialogue: 2,0:41:50.95,0:41:53.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So much difference \NYes, every month
Dialogue: 2,0:41:53.99,0:41:55.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is the difference really that big? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 2,0:41:55.56,0:42:01.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, its a comprehensive use of your image and name \N-I see
Dialogue: 2,0:42:01.86,0:42:05.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what it is
Dialogue: 2,0:42:05.13,0:42:08.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, just give it a go!
Dialogue: 2,0:42:09.27,0:42:11.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That was fast \NSuper fast
Dialogue: 2,0:42:11.81,0:42:15.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But, the menu is cheap. If it's cheap and tasty, people will come in, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:15.48,0:42:17.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think people will come \N-Agreed
Dialogue: 2,0:42:17.36,0:42:19.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Said herself it looks like it will fail
Dialogue: 2,0:42:17.48,0:42:18.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, it is a ready-made store
Dialogue: 2,0:42:19.35,0:42:21.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I choose B \N-Okay, I see
Dialogue: 2,0:42:21.35,0:42:23.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 2,0:42:21.46,0:42:23.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Quick decision!
Dialogue: 2,0:42:23.77,0:42:27.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, the background music
Dialogue: 2,0:42:28.08,0:42:34.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nana Suzuki♪ Nana Suzuki♪ Yakiniku Nana Suzuki♪
Dialogue: 2,0:42:34.48,0:42:37.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ju Ju Ju (the sound of barbecue) One piece into the soul♡
Dialogue: 2,0:42:37.80,0:42:41.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it beef tongue you like? Grilled ribeye?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:41.77,0:42:43.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or me?♪
Dialogue: 2,0:42:43.57,0:42:45.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 2,0:42:45.74,0:42:47.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:47.31,0:42:51.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,People eating will feel tired, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:42:51.75,0:43:00.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like one of those advertising trucks going around Shibuya
Dialogue: 2,0:43:02.02,0:43:04.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Correct answer
Dialogue: 2,0:43:04.63,0:43:08.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For Option A, you will not be paid monthly
Dialogue: 2,0:43:08.80,0:43:12.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Plan B will give you 100,000 yen per month
Dialogue: 2,0:43:12.80,0:43:15.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A big difference
Dialogue: 2,0:43:15.60,0:43:22.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Option B is more compatible with store B. I choose option B \N-Got it
Dialogue: 2,0:43:22.51,0:43:27.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How about a discount when you play this music \N-Good idea!
Dialogue: 2,0:43:28.18,0:43:30.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Personal proposal of a discount program
Dialogue: 2,0:43:31.76,0:43:36.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suzuki ends up with a full package of 1.22 million yen per month
Dialogue: 2,0:43:37.16,0:43:44.33,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0000BA&\move(720,1080,720,875,0,150)}The truth is revealed
Dialogue: 2,0:43:37.90,0:43:44.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what's going on!
Dialogue: 1,0:43:39.42,0:43:40.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How could she also do this
Dialogue: 2,0:43:44.64,0:43:47.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus we explain the project
Dialogue: 2,0:43:49.04,0:43:51.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 2,0:43:51.61,0:43:54.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really, really annoying
Dialogue: 2,0:43:54.21,0:43:57.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What will people think of this?
Dialogue: 2,0:43:57.48,0:44:00.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What if my work is reduced? \NHow much work do you have now?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:00.32,0:44:03.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't make it work if I have less than I already do now
Dialogue: 2,0:44:03.02,0:44:04.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is really unimaginable
Dialogue: 2,0:44:04.52,0:44:10.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2A0DF0&\3c&HFFFFFF&}In summary\N{\c\3c}The next challenge is Yakiniku Asahi Nao
Dialogue: 2,0:44:12.63,0:44:14.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think? \N-So scary
Dialogue: 2,0:44:14.86,0:44:17.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can people change like this?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:17.07,0:44:19.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to switch so easily?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:19.07,0:44:20.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Women of that rank...
Dialogue: 2,0:44:22.74,0:44:27.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the stage of planning, wouldn't producers voice their opinions?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:27.52,0:44:29.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is better and so on
Dialogue: 2,0:44:29.20,0:44:31.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Up until there i thought it was ok...
Dialogue: 2,0:44:31.08,0:44:37.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't let their people just do whatever they want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.52,0:44:39.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 2,0:44:39.09,0:44:41.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But how about if this kind of opportunity really came to you
Dialogue: 2,0:44:41.40,0:44:43.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Would you go along with it?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:43.96,0:44:50.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Wednesday Downtown is a show that is using someone's name
Dialogue: 2,0:44:50.10,0:44:52.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Downtown's \NReally?
Dialogue: 2,0:44:52.22,0:44:56.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Using the Downtown for fraudulent purposes
